items.sentence: I own 30 acres of land about 3 miles out of town.
One thing I like about Tom is his way of talking.
Do you remember what time Tom said he\'d be here?
Do you think you\'re going to be able to stop me?
You\'re three months older than Tom, aren\'t you?
You\'re three years older than I am, aren\'t you?
You\'re three years younger than me, aren\'t you?
You\'re too young to buy cigarettes, aren\'t you?
Do you really think this will ruin my reputation?
How could Tom know that that was going to happen?
